biography.en:
Name (in native language)
嵐田佐和子

An illustrator that has worked primarily with cover art for novels and game character designs, some of them are the Ninja Love and My Sweet Prince installments of NTT Solmare's series of English otome games.

Worked as assistant for Saruwatari Tetsuya.

Alt names:
Ootake Masao
Otake Masao
おおたけまさお
大武政夫
